Send a claim form to your [local Jobcentre Plus.](http://los.direct.gov.uk/default.aspx?type=1&lang=en "find your local Jobcentre Plus office"){:rel="external"}

$D
[Download 'SF500 - Budgeting Loan claim form - England, Wales or Scotland' (PDF, 135KB)](http://www.dwp.gov.uk/advisers/claimforms/sf500_print.pdf "Download 'Budgeting Loan claim form - England, Wales or Scotland' (PDF, 135KB)"){:rel="external"}
$D

